```java
mRunnable = () -&gt; {
   yourButton.onClick();
   mHandler.postDelayed(mRunnable, seconds * 1000);
}

mHandler = new Handler();
```

3. You need to also start the handler. So, use this to start it. I&#39;d prefer to use this in `onCreate()`:
```java
mHandler.postDelayed(mRunnable, seconds * 1000);
```

